title: アオハル杯3戦目・次は勝てるもん！

text.jpText:
負けてしまっても、ポジティブなハルウララ。
次は絶対に勝てるから、期待してて欲しいと
明るく言ってのけるのだった。
text.enText:
Even though they lost, Haruurara is positive. 
She said cheerfully, "We will definitely win 
next time, so please keep your expectations 
high. She said cheerfully, "We will 
definitely win next time.
